# Document AI - BatchInputConfig
This item is deprecated!The message for input config in batch process.| JSON representation       |
|:----------------------------------------------|
| { "gcsSource": string, "mimeType": string } || Fields | Fields.1                                                     |
|:----------|:--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| gcsSource | string The Cloud Storage location as the source of the document.                                       |
| mimeType | string An IANA published media type (MIME type) of the input. If the input is a raw document, refer to supported file types for the list of media types. If the input is a Document, the type should be application/json.
